{"tid":393271,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人用過salbutamol氣管舒張噴劑","createTime":"2017-09-09T06:24:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-09T09:48:31.000Z","uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"67481cd925cb5710b7a85e28616c0b1cdad1ea12","tid":393271,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T06:24:06.000Z","msg":"我唔知點解<br />\n個人一累, 上樓梯少少扯到條氣都會唔舒服<br />\n同埋好多其他野同醫生講左,<br />\n所以醫生開左salbutamol有需要時用<br />\n<br />\n想問你地係咩事所以要用<br />\n用完有冇覺得好左<br />\n有冇特別嚴重副作用<br />\nThx"},{"pid":"44e2b481e4e25ddbd26318d0d89adddb378a4998","tid":393271,"uid":41849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T06:26:06.000Z","msg":"一般用冇咩野"},{"pid":"90d4fa7e25bcefd6bad2a481ec55346fff2710c1","tid":393271,"uid":133319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T06:26:43.000Z","msg":"唔噴多就無嘢"},{"pid":"655bddea649cf5f009ac29db2becbf62c34a8c50","tid":393271,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T06:27:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一般用冇咩野</blockquote><br />\n其實我唔知係咩事<br />\n又唔知關唔關事"},{"pid":"0f31921601a6c6b30ac68784a864c1a575c0c55d","tid":393271,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T06:27:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔噴多就無嘢</blockquote><br />\n琴晚第一次用, 噴左兩下<br />\n<br />\n岩岩行左幾分鐘路出去食野,<br />\n個人又開始浮<br />\n所以又噴左兩下<br />\n<br />\n其實我唔知自己咩事"},{"pid":"7dc4663056d09aac7d95b86a3f3f45486c21aa51","tid":393271,"uid":46197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T06:29:58.000Z","msg":"噴多會心跳快"},{"pid":"5816c88296d1d475307579a866e06d787e4f712d","tid":393271,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T06:31:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>噴多會心跳快</blockquote><br />\n我覺得自己心臟本身就唔係幾好"},{"pid":"4f62f0ee8a4bf5268c4635e8532084ba3b1e166d","tid":393271,"uid":4596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T06:32:42.000Z","msg":"Short acting beta 2 agonist 通常都係比哮喘嘅人用(如果我冇記錯)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68fa0fa7a87f868b8d5686d1f1d17b31d907d93b","tid":393271,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T06:35:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Short acting beta 2 agonist 通常都係比哮喘嘅人用(如果我冇記錯)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我就係唔知自己咩事<br />\n中定西醫好<br />\n西醫普通檢查 心電圖 心肺x光 果d做過晒 都冇事<br />\n醫生聽呼吸又話唔似真哮喘"},{"pid":"761081ab8a2f92e95bb3a6d3351c192b31901915","tid":393271,"uid":653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T06:41:38.000Z","msg":"老豆用左好多年<br />\n都無咩野，上樓梯前吸一二口"},{"pid":"7db28f91b032901041618cb302d60dc0743ce2d7","tid":393271,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T06:48:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老豆用左好多年<br />\n都無咩野，上樓梯前吸一二口</blockquote><br />\n我下次想試下<br />\n上樓梯之前吸吸, 睇下會唔會好d<br />\n<br />\n做帶氧運動半年我心肺竟然仲差左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6411c794cf26b175a1eef2e0af63b9e25c5b1413","tid":393271,"uid":48572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T06:54:55.000Z","msg":"游水有幫助"},{"pid":"2febefd3e7ff05ca51d0619f583ef5891fbf6317","tid":393271,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T06:58:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>游水有幫助</blockquote><br />\n跑步機有冇"},{"pid":"0352bb72b3dd5b920f6b6f8ebaf75690232fa750","tid":393271,"uid":653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T09:48:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>老豆用左好多年<br />\n都無咩野，上樓梯前吸一二口</blockquote><br />\n我下次想試下<br />\n上樓梯之前吸吸, 睇下會唔會好d<br />\n<br />\n做帶氧運動半年我心肺竟然仲差左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做下伸展運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一吸一呼咁做"}]}